Class GuestMember

java.lang.Object
User
GuestMember
public class GuestMember extends User
The GuestMember class simulates a guest to the library and is as subclass to the User superclass. The guestMember has set priveleges compared to the LibraryMember class in that it only has 3 Days of library access
